headline: Australia Wireless Router Market Trends Report 2025-2033 | Wi-Fi 6, Smart Home Appliances and Remote Work Drive Demand
summary: The Australia wireless router market is projected to grow from US$ 267.34 million in 2024 to US$ 559.4 million by 2033, at a CAGR of 8.55% from 2025 to 2033. Key growth drivers include increased internet penetration, the rise of smart home devices, remote work trends, and advances in Wi-Fi technology like Wi-Fi 6. These factors necessitate high-performance routers for better connectivity and speed. Additionally, the expansion of the National Broadband Network boosts demand. Market challenges inc

headline: Mountain Valley MD Holdings Announces Changes to Board of Directors
summary: TORONTO, July 24, 2025--Mountain Valley MD Holdings Inc. (the "Company" or "MVMD") (CSE: MVMD) (OTCQB: MVMDF) (FRA: 20MP) is pleased to announce the appointment of David Batchelor to its board of directors.
